         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/4/84 ¶  ¶ Today the post brings me the enclosed card, dear Krichauff, for the good old Mr Fischer, ¶ Krichauff's father-in-law, Ludwig Fischer.Card not found. ¶  ¶ from Garden Inspector Ohrt, who wr...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">84.04.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">1/4/84</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heute bringt mir die Post beigefügte Karte, lieber Krichauff, für den guten alten Herrn Fischer, von Herrn Garten-Inspector Ohrt, der dabei schreibt "Beifolgende Karte haben Sie wohl die Güte, meinem hochverehrten alten Lehrherrn, Herrn Fischer gelegentlich zuzusenden."</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich schreibe bald wieder an Herrn Ohrt, so dass ich irgend eine Bestellung an ihn recht gern übernehmen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoffentlich seid Ihr Alle recht munter u wohl, u geht es Dir auch geschäftlich recht gut.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Stets der Deine</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/4/84</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Today the post brings me the enclosed card, dear Krichauff, for the good old Mr Fischer,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Krichauff's father-in-law, Ludwig Fischer.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Card not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from Garden Inspector Ohrt, who writes at the same time: "Will you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have the goodness to send the following card<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>at your convenience<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to my esteemed old master, Mr Fischer."</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will write to Mr Ohrt again soon, so that I will be quite happy to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>accept any message<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to him.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope you are all well and happy, and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>also<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that your business is going well.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Always<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
